{"tid":562921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"樂施會的「羅馬帝國性愛派對」 半祼女災民跑來跑去","createTime":"2018-02-16T11:21:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-16T12:15:00.000Z","uid":72009,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3572513ed9109a46b8b10e94d8867a99d33e287a","tid":562921,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T11:21:09.000Z","msg":"2010年海地地震造成多達22萬人死亡、30萬人受傷以及150萬人陷於貧窮，樂施會以人道救援為名，在當地展開大型救災行動。不過在救災的同時，部分救援人員卻被揭發在災區進行令人髮指行為。<br />\n<br />\n一群男性前線救援人員利用組織租用的住所開淫亂派對。該住所被稱為「粉紅住宅」或是「妓院」。<br />\n<br />\n曾經看過淫亂派對影片的消息人士描述：「這些女孩穿上樂施會的T恤，半裸地跑來跑去。那就像羅馬帝國皇帝卡利古拉（Caligula）的狂歡派對。令人難以置信，那是瘋狂的行為。」有消息更指淫亂派對涉及雛妓，她們年僅約14至16歲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想起淫蕩畫面"},{"pid":"948b8744ed1c5d57bcfc6518afcf183d6d9b00d5","tid":562921,"uid":48889,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T11:22:04.000Z","msg":"屌 冇圖"},{"pid":"ab0cdf8a124b2af848a0bb98f48dfc8c899e1de4","tid":562921,"uid":50328,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T11:23:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"da70a1cef9561dd2966b9d0047f577344c4d815e","tid":562921,"uid":34410,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"948b8744ed1c5d57bcfc6518afcf183d6d9b00d5","tid":562921,"uid":48889,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T11:22:04.000Z","msg":"屌 冇圖"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T11:23:09.000Z","msg":"黑力架都要睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"171f03dd3aabab08d1a9a8e1f535cf1ffa23e728","tid":562921,"uid":97080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T11:24:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b3e83e721f96c9ebe3823dd02ad0debcfdf24f2","tid":562921,"uid":82175,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T11:24:28.000Z","msg":"施比受更有福 樂施會班人有福啦"},{"pid":"c1b3523266d3bc6448d59672ad0ddea2174d50de","tid":562921,"uid":72009,"like":0,"d